PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776985387
OL,3,CLewis Moody 'takes the baton' from
OL,4,CDoddie Weir and Rob Burrow in MND fight
OL,6,FOf Wilkinson, Moody notes: "He's
OL,7,Fprobably hired a group of people to
OL,8,Fget him ready for the conditioning
OL,9,Fside of it. I dread to think how he's
OL,10,Fgoing to turn up looking. Is there a
OL,11,Fbike strong enough to withstand the
OL,12,Fpower he can put through it?"
OL,14,FLike Weir and Burrow before him, you
OL,15,Fjust sense that Moody will do all he
OL,16,Fcan, for as long as he can, to
OL,17,Fconfound the cruel hand he's been
OL,18,Fdealt; not just for himself and his
OL,19,Ffamily, but for those who come after
OL,20,Fhim receiving this life-changing
OL,21,Fdiagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
